derlying\nblockchain, Setchain objects can be used as a sidechain to implement many\ndecentralized solutions with much faster operations than direct implementations\non top of blockchains. Finally, we also present an algorithm that encompasses\nin a single process the combined behavior of Byzantine servers, which\nsimplifies correctness proofs by encoding the general attacker in a concrete\nimplementation.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 9 Feb 2023 16:25:31 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-02-10"}
