_N$ as well as of the VED. This is in\nagreement with recent studies suggesting that the combination of these two\nfeatures can be favorable for a possible resolution of the $\\sigma_8$ and $H_0$\ntensions. In this work, we show that the Brans-Dicke theory with running vacuum\nhas the potential to alleviate the two tensions at the same time.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 9 Feb 2023 17:52:50 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-02-10"}
