forms closely to IPD. Finally, we apply our method to develop\na high dimensional genetic risk model for type II diabetes using large-scale\nbiobank data sets from UK Biobank and Mass General Brigham, where only a small\nfraction of subjects from the latter has been labeled via chart reviewing.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 9 Feb 2023 23:09:00 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-02-13"}
