ice. Numerical results demonstrate\nthe effectiveness of our PSO-assisted re-initialization strategy in achieving\nthe global optimality, and the superiority of our method over its competitor in\nterms of positioning accuracy.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 10 Feb 2023 09:01:19 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-02-13"}
