ined with Probabilistic Programming Languages to\nperform posterior inference with state-of-the-art algorithms including a No\nU-Turn Sampler, Automatic Differentiation Variational Inference,and Neural\nTransport HMC. We further demonstrate that Normalizing Flows using Neural\nTransport are a promising methodology for model validation in the early stages\nof analysis.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 10 Feb 2023 10:40:19 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 27 Apr 2023 12:57:02 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-05-01"}
